headline: Goldman Sachs Group (GS) Advises F&F Co. Ltd. In TaylorMade Acquisition Plan
summary: Goldman Sachs Group (GS) recently saw a 33% price increase, potentially influenced by its new role as financial advisor to F&F Co. Ltd. for TaylorMade's acquisition. This association may have enhanced the company's market perception, supporting its robust Q2 earnings report where net income rose to USD 3,723 million. Additionally, the appointment of Raghav Maliah as Chairman of Investment Banking reinforces confidence in leadership. Amid market conditions that saw mixed movements in indexes...
